Hi all

This map was created by me
Its a fun map with many barricading spots around the map and some harder to reach places
it is designed to support up to 64 players and runs very smoothly
it also has 5 secret areas
3 of the secrets are walls u can walk through
1 of them is a teleport (hidden)
the last 1 is a breakable floor somewhere

see if u can spot the secrets

There is a code panel to get into the reactor the code is as follows [1] - [5] - [4] - [2]
The reactor has a function where it can be destroyed 
once u destroy the reactor it will turn off all the lights and make all the doors inoperable but on the plus side there is a back up reactor to turn on the emergency lighting

try it out and see how well u do

and good hunting hope you have fun

this map is decompile protected sorry but i like to keep my work protected

This map was tested on the =UKLP= Zombiemod server and is now hosted on that server due to people liking it
